{"tid":442232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應羅哲斯被拒入境香港　中方召見英大使提嚴正交涉","createTime":"2017-10-20T12:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T01:39:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"924b7fe058aa252b5bb0dfc7c82853bdff055478","tid":442232,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171020/s00004/3d9f64b7fbe81d0c33f8629d9dadeea3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171020%2Fs00004%2F3d9f64b7fbe81d0c33f8629d9dadeea3.jpg&h=f7efa40d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權領袖羅哲斯（Bendict Rogers）被拒入境香港，英國國會及外交部均表關注，早前已傳召中國駐英國大使解釋事件；首相文翠珊亦揚言會循「不同層面」解決事件。中國外交部星期五在北京舉行例會，發言人陸慷重申，香港事務純屬中國內政，中方不會允許任何外國政府、機構和個人，以任何方式干涉內政。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷強調，香港屬中國特別行政區，中央政府負責香港外交事務；北京政府和特區政府依法處置有關問題，「允許誰入境，不允許誰入境，是中國的主權」。他透露北京已召見英國駐華大使，就英方近來一系列錯誤言論提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n（中新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171020/s00004/1508495943806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171020%2Fs00004%2F1508495943806&d=rNlrB5lgYtay0WU3ziUhLzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=70b6df98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171020%2Fs00004%2F1508495943806&h=553ca80d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171020/s00004/1508495943806</a>"},{"pid":"06dca53d13e0433af07b671c7d3ef570f8b28348","tid":442232,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"口交部今次又係呢兩套板斧<br />\n有種既就直接唔好比英國人入你境內囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70de6cf6508bd0894d9c8f40252d91a46358d6ce","tid":442232,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a6